## Project Structure

```
src/
├── controllers/       # HTTP request handlers (thin layer)
│   ├── billingController.ts   # Billing + Ledger + DLQ endpoints
│   ├── rateController.ts
│   ├── stripeController.ts
│   ├── usageController.ts     # CDR ingestion with DLQ integration
│   └── userController.ts
├── services/          # Business logic (billing engine)
│   ├── billingService.ts      # Atomic billing, ledger, Banker's Rounding
│   └── deadLetterService.ts   # Dead Letter Queue management
├── models/            # Database schema definitions
│   └── User.ts                # All CREATE TABLE statements (users, logs, bills, ledger, DLQ)
├── routes/            # Express route definitions + Swagger docs
├── middleware/        # Auth, error handling, security, roles
├── database/          # Connection pool configuration
├── errors/            # Custom error classes (AppError)
├── types/             # TypeScript interfaces
├── utils/             # Logger, validation helpers
├── index.ts           # App entry point
└── swagger.ts         # Swagger schema definitions
docs/
└── ARCHITECTURE.md    # System diagrams (data flow, ERD, deployment)
tests/
├── controllers/       # Controller unit tests
└── services/          # Service unit tests (billing precision)
k8s/                   # Kubernetes manifests (deployment, HPA, ingress)
```

